trajectories of vortices. The obtained results of\nthe jet penetration height are presented as a power law correlation. The\nresults of this study show that the designed setup using a low-cost LED and\nlow-cost control system is a high potential option for application in\nvisualization studies of high speed flows.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2016 17:55:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 07:54:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-29"}
